{"tid":1469383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"發夢見到機場站多人到爆","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:29:16.000Z","uid":212412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30fffabe31510156aa114082d4d48ce64e634635","tid":1469383,"uid":212412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:39:30.000Z","msg":"仲夢見機場快線好多人搭呀，多到啲人要企喺張凳度先逼到上車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我就逼唔上，上唔到車要等多幾班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連我喺預辦登機啲行李都delay 埋，去唔到機場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae77556e4568fcc973def49536d32bec8de350e1","tid":1469383,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:40:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f292ef3b318b7d7017f788a436e00c7c5671aae5